Well, <i>vive la difference.</i>

215
00:14:49,021 --> 00:14:51,649
On the last page
of <i>Huis Clos,</i>

216
00:14:51,757 --> 00:14:55,659
who can tell me what Sartre meant
when he said " Hell is other people"?

217
00:14:55,761 --> 00:14:58,286
[Sabrina Laughing]

