weird to see her there.

267
00:18:17,496 --> 00:18:19,987
Huh. That is weird.

268
00:18:21,934 --> 00:18:25,495
My mom and I
are so close.

269
00:18:25,604 --> 00:18:29,165
- We're more like sisters.
<i>- You're so lucky.</i>

270
00:18:31,076 --> 00:18:34,375
