<i>Continues]</i>

347
00:24:12,884 --> 00:24:15,876
<i>[Tina] I don't know.</i>
<i>Jimmy, just tell me what to do.</i>

348
00:24:21,393 --> 00:24:23,759
Curfew, girls.

349
00:24:23,862 --> 00:24:27,889
