409
00:28:37,782 --> 00:28:41,377
Yeah, right.

410
00:28:42,220 --> 00:28:45,712
No, really.
I only did it once.

411
00:28:48,093 --> 00:28:50,425
Where'd you do it?

412
00:28:50,528 --> 00:28:52,462
On the beach.

413
00:28:52,564 --> 00:28:55,226
You're kidding!

414
00:28:56,835 --> 00:29:00,066
- Did it hurt?
<i>- No.</i>

415
00:29:00,171 --> 00:29:03,004
It was great.

