<i>I thought maybe it would be good...</i>

426
00:30:08,139 --> 00:30:12,906
if maybe, ah, Sabrina
was nominated for president too.

427
00:30:13,011 --> 00:30:14,979
That's so sweet, Ellie.

428
00:30:15,079 --> 00:30:19,277
